The 3rd Annual Central Washington University Northwest Center for Sport Summit was a huge success 🙌🏼

Honoured to have been asked to be the keynote speaker at this event 🎤

Sharing my journey is important to me 🏈

My mission has always been to inspire future female professionals in the world of sport! 

 Thank you to @central_washington_university for having me and Sean Dahlin for being a great support through the planning and process. What a great event!

WFC Speaker, Coach @amandaruller, has created a ‘Football Playbook for Coaches!’ 🏈 It’s a 100-page notebook with field diagrams for drawing plays, creating drills, and for scouting.
